1) Create .vimrc (first time) 
set expandtab
set tabstop=2
set shiftwidth=2
set softtabstop=2
set autoindent
set smartindent

2) $ source .vimrc (first time)

3) Do the following from the top directory of DFT-FE 
$ find . -name \*.cc -o -name \*.cu -o -name \*.h | xargs -I {} ./indent/indent-with-vim.sh {}
